  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] All of a sudden, an order came that everybody should go back to the tent and to pick up their things that they have surrendered.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We didn't know what happened, so we went back, we picked up whatever there was, and we were marched back to our barracks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So the rumor was that we will be left with our own civilian clothes and the idea was apparently-- now, these were all rumors-- that we are going to be kept for eventual trade for some trucks or coffee and that type of thing.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Nothing was confirmed or officially announced.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were left with our own clothes and, well, that was it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were put into those barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from then on, so every morning we would get something that looked like coffee.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And around noon time, we would get a turnip soup, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a thick turnip soup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at night, again, we would get a little bit of that ersatz cafe, you know, coffee substitution.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From time-- Were you with any friends?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were you're with people that you knew?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You made friends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You made friends, although I did have some people-- as a matter of fact, I got to know some people in the orphanage that we came together in the-- from the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the whole group, that 4,500 people or so, were billeted in several barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they consisted primarily of highly intellectual people, mostly from Budapest, and doctors, lawyers, professors, writers, actors, you name it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were-- we managed to sort of survive on-- every night somebody would give us a little pep talk of some sort.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were hermetically enclosed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know what was going on in the outside world at all.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
